  "subject": "Add support setting/showing 'required' field for custom properties",
  "commit_message": "Add support setting/showing 'required' field for custom properties\n\nUser may want to set required to true for their custom property.\nThis change adds checkbox to Add Property dialog to set required field\nand also adds new column in properties list to show required field.\n\nChange-Id: I035feb34a7395ca664a9b0ed54e955baac3a7e14\nIssue-ID: SDC-2659\nSigned-off-by: Satoshi Fujii <fujii-satoshi@jp.fujitsu.com>\n",
